@startuml
participant ThreadA
participant ConcurrentHashMap
participant ThreadB
ThreadA -> ConcurrentHashMap: put(key, newValue)  // CAS 更新
ConcurrentHashMap --> ThreadA: success
ThreadB -> ConcurrentHashMap: get(key)  // 可能看到 oldValue (不一致窗口)
ConcurrentHashMap --> ThreadB: oldValue
note right of ConcurrentHashMap: 最终一致：稍后 ThreadB 会看到 newValue
@enduml